        "description": {
            "name": "description",
            "type": "java.lang.String",
            "value": "Zend_Db_Table->insert() is not compatible with one of the latest changes in Zend_Db_Adapter_Abstract, and causes this exception to be thrown when called:\n\n\"You must not specify a sequence to lastInsertId() in this adapter\"\n\nline 241 from\n\n  return $this->_db->lastInsertId($this->_name, $this->_primary);\n\nto\n\n  return $this->_db->lastInsertId();\n\nseem to solve the problem, but I am not sure if this is the right fix."
        },
